{"tid":2470302,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國呼籲世界對中國採取強硬態度","createTime":"2021-03-31T23:34:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T14:08:56.000Z","uid":229777,"like":96,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"467831306fd88d2ce23ebb7b785e68149a387f60","tid":2470302,"uid":229777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-31T23:34:47.000Z","msg":"英國國際貿易部大臣卓慧思(Liz Truss)呼籲世界應對中國採取強硬態度<br />\n<br />\n作為G7嘅主席國，卓慧思正呼籲美國幫手改革世貿，並指出所有改革都必須要對中國採取強硬態度。佢指出世貿成立時中國係美國經濟嘅10%，宜家仲好似嗰時咁話白己係發展中國家簡直荒謬，必須要改<br />\n<br />\n佢指出如果世貿唔改革，其他國家就會用其他途徑發展貿易，宜家係時候對中國及其喺國際貿易上嘅行為採取強硬態度，並令世貿變得現代化<br />\n<br />\n佢希望英國可以喺今年內加入CPTPP，並稱印度係佢未來想有trade deal嘅重點候選國<br />\n<br />\n英國未放棄同美國簽trade deal，但美國此刻就興趣唔大<br />\n<br />\n英國認為未來仍要同中國喺非戰略範疇內進行貿易，但並無同中國簽trade deal 嘅打算 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.ft.com/__origami/service/image/v2/images/raw/https%3A%2F%2Fd1e00ek4ebabms.cloudfront.net%2Fproduction%2F1b01ffc3-ad64-478a-8c32-9a482612b0e0.jpg?fit=scale-down&amp;source=next&amp;width=700\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2F__origami%2Fservice%2Fimage%2Fv2%2Fimages%2Fraw%2Fhttps%253A%252F%252Fd1e00ek4ebabms.cloudfront.net%252Fproduction%252F1b01ffc3-ad64-478a-8c32-9a482612b0e0.jpg%3Ffit%3Dscale-down%26source%3Dnext%26width%3D700&h=430f6456&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英文全文: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ft.com/content/5775b176-aff3-4d34-bea4-1566e11b315e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F5775b176-aff3-4d34-bea4-1566e11b315e&d=6VUJY1vbA2ifZxBcTMZdIzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=4347fe29\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ft.com/content/5775b176-aff3-4d34-bea4-1566e11b315e</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">3月31號文章，非愚人節 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"5fbe713d9539a2f842cfc36fd55e37dd8568fe9e","tid":2470302,"uid":283130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-31T23:35:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class